---
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro';
import { AUTHOR, SOCIAL, TOPIC_PILLARS } from '../consts';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="OneMoreTechie is a Principal Cloud Architect and DevSecOps leader sharing production-grade tutorials on AWS, DevOps, Cloud Architecture, Security, and IaC & Kubernetes."
>
  <header class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-avatar" aria-hidden="true">{AUTHOR.initials}</div>
    <div>
      <div class="section-label">About</div>
      <h1 class="about-h1">Behind the tutorials</h1>
      <p class="about-role">{AUTHOR.role}, writing under the <strong>{AUTHOR.name}</strong> banner.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="about-lede">
    <p>
      OneMoreTechie is a tutorial channel + blog by a Principal Cloud Architect and
      DevSecOps leader working across AWS at scale — daily reality that shapes every
      post here. The goal: share what actually works in production, not what looks
      good in a slide deck.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every article pairs with a companion YouTube video and, where relevant, a live
      GitHub repo with runnable code. Readers get a choice of medium; the same
      source material feeds interview prep, on-the-job reference, and self-directed
      learning.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-block">
    <div class="section-label">What you'll find here</div>
    <h2 class="about-h2">Five topic pillars</h2>
    <p class="about-sub">
      Each pillar is a durable subject area — the ones I work in daily and can speak
      to with production experience, not tutorial regurgitation.
    </p>
    <ul class="pillars-list">
      {TOPIC_PILLARS.map((p) => (
        <li>
          <a class={`pillar-tile pill-${p.color}`} href={`/topics/${p.slug}/`}>
            <span class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">{p.icon}</span>
            <span class="pillar-label">{p.label}</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="about-block">
    <div class="section-label">Content medium</div>
    <h2 class="about-h2">Blog, YouTube, GitHub — same source</h2>
    <div class="medium-grid">
      <div class="medium-card">
        <div class="medium-icon" aria-hidden="true">📝</div>
        <div class="medium-label">Blog</div>
        <p class="medium-desc">Written deep-dives — searchable, linkable, editable as knowledge evolves.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-card">
        <div class="medium-icon" aria-hidden="true">▶</div>
        <div class="medium-label">YouTube</div>
        <p class="medium-desc">Screen-recorded walkthroughs of the same content, for readers who prefer video.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-card">
        <div class="medium-icon" aria-hidden="true">◍</div>
        <div class="medium-label">GitHub</div>
        <p class="medium-desc">Runnable code companion to the tutorials — Terraform, Helm, playbooks, sample apps.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-block">
    <div class="section-label">Connect</div>
    <h2 class="about-h2">Subscribe or follow along</h2>
    <p class="about-sub">
      The channel and blog publish on the same cadence. Comments and pull requests
      on the code repos are welcome.
    </p>
    <ul class="social-links">
      <li><a class="social-btn" href={SOCIAL.youtube} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span aria-hidden="true">▶</span> YouTube
      </a></li>
      <li><a class="social-btn" href={SOCIAL.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span aria-hidden="true">◍</span> GitHub
      </a></li>
      <li><a class="social-btn" href={SOCIAL.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span aria-hidden="true">in</span> LinkedIn
      </a></li>
      <li><a class="social-btn" href={SOCIAL.twitter} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span aria-hidden="true">X</span> Twitter
      </a></li>
      <li><a class="social-btn" href="/rss.xml">
        <span aria-hidden="true">📡</span> RSS
      </a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <style>
    .about-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      gap: 1.75rem;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: var(--bg2);
      border: 1px solid var(--line2);
      border-radius: var(--rl);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .about-avatar {
      width: 72px; height: 72px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--purple) 100%);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-family: var(--fh);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--bg);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .about-h1 {
      font-family: var(--fh);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.15;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 0.25rem 0 0.4rem;
    }
    .about-role {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .about-lede { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .about-lede p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--text2);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      max-width: 720px;
    }
    .about-block {
      padding-top: 2.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .about-h2 {
      font-family: var(--fh);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 0.35rem 0 0.6rem;
    }
    .about-sub {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text2);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Pillar tiles */
    .pillars-list {
      list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .pillar-tile {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: var(--r);
      border: 1px solid;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.18s;
    }
    .pillar-tile:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); color: inherit; }
    .pillar-icon {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      width: 34px; height: 34px;
      border-radius: var(--r);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }
    :global([data-theme="light"]) .pillar-tile .pillar-icon {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    }
    .pillar-label {
      font-family: var(--fh);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: inherit;
    }

    /* Medium (blog/YT/GitHub) grid */
    .medium-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .medium-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: var(--bg2);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--rl);
    }
    .medium-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border-radius: var(--r);
      background: var(--adim);
      color: var(--accent);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    }
    .medium-label {
      font-family: var(--fh);
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .medium-desc {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text2);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* Social */
    .social-links {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0; margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .social-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      background: var(--bg2);
      border: 1px solid var(--line2);
      border-radius: var(--r);
      font-family: var(--fh);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.18s;
    }
    .social-btn > span {
      display: inline-flex;
      width: 20px; height: 20px;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      background: var(--adim);
      color: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .social-btn:hover {
      border-color: var(--abdr);
      background: var(--bg3);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .pillars-list { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .medium-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .pillars-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .about-hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: left; }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
